        "هِ اَلرَّجُلُ قَالَ «نَعَمْ إِنَّمَا يُكْرَهُ اَلْمُلْحَمُ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2606 - Laith al-Muradi asked Imam (as) about a man entering Ihram in an embroidered garment.\nImam (as) said: \"Yes, it is permissible. What is disliked is a fully patterned garment (mulham).\""
        ]
